<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    table { border-collapse: collapse; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
    th { background: #1f4e79; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 700; }
    th, td { border: 1px solid #9ca3af; padding: 8px 10px; }
    .note { background: #fff2cc; font-weight: 700; padding: 8px 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; display: inline-block; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="note">Template Import Siswa. Isi data pada baris kosong di bawah header. Kolom wajib: nisn, nama, kelas, jk. Status: Aktif, Cuti, Pindah, atau Drop Out. Password boleh dikosongkan agar dibuat otomatis.</div>
  <table>
    <tr>
      <th>nisn</th>
      <th>nama</th>
      <th>kelas</th>
      <th>jk</th>
      <th>status</th>
      <th>password</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td></td>
      <td></td>
      <td></td>
      <td></td>
      <td>Aktif</td>
      <td></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td></td>
      <td></td>
      <td></td>
      <td></td>
      <td>Aktif</td>
      <td></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td></td>
      <td></td>
      <td></td>
      <td></td>
      <td>Aktif</td>
      <td></td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
